These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, sailing
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | thriller |
| Sport       | baseball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, blend
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, security-guard
1. the security-guard is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
2. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | blend |
| Job      | security-guard     | musician  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, turquise
City: rome, miami
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Color   | brown | turquise  |
| City   | rome | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, video-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, crime
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Hobby   | video-games | puzzles   |
| Movie-Genre       | crime | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
