The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily
1. the person who growslily is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| City   | berlin    | san-francisco    |
| Flower   | bellflower | lily |

